body:
You could define a module like this:
```
class View(nn.Module):
       def __init__(self):
            super(View, self).__init__()
   
        def forward(self, x):
            return x.view(-1) 
```

This flattens the input but similarly you could provide a size object.

Now you can use this as part of the model.
